CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 19, 1974, pg. 18 reads: "Contemplating - Two local young men who enjoy a game of chess are "Bones" Taylor and Raymond Hart. They compare strategies here while participating in chess, the king of all games to many. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: "Bones" Taylor and Raymond Hart playing chess on fuzzy chess board with another man watching
